question: Within a radius of 180 kilometers, what fast food restaurant is available located en route to the Mexican Museum, San Francisco, CA from San Jose State University, San Jose, CA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-121.879994 37.33896)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.430775 37.806821)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-121.879994 37.33896)',4326)::geography, 180000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-121.879994 37.33896)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
